From 8:30 a.m. to 2:30 p.m. Monday through Friday Feb. 22-26 users of the SR 305 Agate Pass Bridge are encouraged to plan for significant congestion. During a 5-day inspection the bridge will be reduced to one alternating lane of traffic. Travelers can expect at least 30-minute delays especially later in the day.
